Mac-iTunes-Item version 0.01
==========================

A representation of a single item within an iTunes library.

This modules provides a data structure for representing a item (song, URL,
video) within an iTunes library.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None!

